OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClearer
OL,6,Fskies for many overnight which will
OL,7,Fallow temperatures to fall, giving a
OL,8,Fmuch more comfortable night for many.
OL,9,FStaying dry with mist and fog in
OL,10,Fplaces.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FMist and fog clearing to
OL,13,Fleave bright and sunny spells for
OL,14,Fmany. Staying very warm for the time
OL,15,Fof year but temperatures slightly
OL,16,Flower than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
