OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FScattered showers and sunny spells on
OL,7,FSunday. Continuing into Monday with
OL,8,Frain, possible thunderstorms. Staying
OL,9,Funsettled through the week as
OL,10,Ftemperatures return to average.
